        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="main-and-aside r">
    <div class="main" role="main">

    <div class="article-teaser">
        Long-term trend of improving Tube performance. Train services up and reliability improves. Passenger satisfaction scores rising according to independent surveys.
        
    </div>



<div class="pull-quote">
        <div class="quote-body">"We are putting in additional measures to continue to improve our performance and deliver an increasingly reliable service"</div>
        <div class="quote-footer">
            <div class="quotee-name">Mike Brown</div>
